	<h3 class="c11">
		<a name="h.y1i58nbp7n2s"></a><span>2.4 Search Order Process</span>
	</h3>
	<p class="c11">
		<span class="c0">From the search page, user enter the order
			number and surname then click the search button. The browser send the
			request </span><span class="c0 c4">action search </span><span class="c0">and
		</span><span class="c0 c4">orderid and surname</span><span class="c0">&nbsp;to
			the servlet </span><span class="c0 c4">OrderController.</span><span
			class="c0">&nbsp;In the </span><span class="c0 c4">OrderController</span><span
			class="c0">, the </span><span class="c0 c4">Order </span><span
			class="c0">and</span><span class="c0 c4">&nbsp;Customer Model
		</span><span class="c0">will be instantiated by connecting to the
			Database then retrieve the info via orderid and surname. After
			instantiating successfully </span><span class="c0 c4">Models</span><span
			class="c0">, the </span><span class="c0 c4">OrderController </span><span
			class="c0">send the </span><span class="c0 c4">Order</span><span
			class="c0">&nbsp;and </span><span class="c0 c4">Customer</span><span
			class="c0">&nbsp;object to the </span><span class="c0 c4">MainController</span><span
			class="c0">. From there, the </span><span class="c0 c4">MainController
		</span><span class="c0">dispatches the object &nbsp;back to the </span><span
			class="c0 c4">View</span><span class="c0">&nbsp;JSP file which
			is </span><span class="c0 c4">search_result.jsp</span><span class="c0">.
			In order to display cart information, the </span><span class="c0 c4">search.jsp</span><span
			class="c0">&nbsp;</span><span class="c0 c4">View </span><span
			class="c0">will invoke back to the </span><span class="c0 c4">Order
			and Customer</span><span class="c0">&nbsp;</span><span class="c0 c4">Model
		</span><span class="c0">to retrieve the product info. Finally, the </span><span
			class="c0 c4">search.jsp</span><span class="c0">&nbsp;</span><span
			class="c0 c4">View </span><span class="c0">responses the
			information to the client browser and display them.</span>
	</p>
